{"tid":661784,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"連登應唔應開個 Trump （侵侵）台？","createTime":"2018-05-12T00:57:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-12T12:09:48.000Z","uid":108201,"like":68,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"0c9115585614d46522dfee4776c4f177c9e3e6b4","tid":661784,"uid":108201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T00:57:35.000Z","msg":"每日Trump 都鼓勵大家連登仔去對抗強權，只計尋日同今日，佢又做左幾件其他元首做幾年做唔出嘅事：<br />\n<br />\n1. 打電話去習廢帝話要劉鶴幾時黎傾trade war，贏國連反對都唔敢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n2. 係國會推動全面考慮禁售晶片比贏國，贏國華為，中興，聯想，海康威視，歌爾聲學立即收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n3. 係北韓救番三個美國人回家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n4. 一比ISIS寸下，十二小時後就捉Q曬ISIS首領<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n5. 正式同大藥廠輝瑞 Merck等等開戰，解救全球病人藥費之苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n只係上述五項，其他國家元首就一世做唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/12/085221_da6f02bb482bb7c6cc965462062f2d8b.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F12%2F085221_da6f02bb482bb7c6cc965462062f2d8b.gif&h=58d0baf2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n贊成開台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：作為連登仔，一定日日支持侵侵打尻贏國同其他強權<br />\n反對開台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：作為一個五毛，點可以比侵侵日日打我們的習帝臉"},{"pid":"954be4f16c309b5119609d685bb1ecc3edc01964","tid":661784,"uid":108201,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T01:28:32.000Z","msg":"自推一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/12/092829_a182bbedae65e5e31fa3893be6881623.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F12%2F092829_a182bbedae65e5e31fa3893be6881623.png&h=c07487ea&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"396bd40f838dc76d94de016ffb329921ebf179b9","tid":661784,"uid":46896,"like":7,"dislike":9,"score":-2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T01:38:59.000Z","msg":"應該，開個台俾侵啲支持者打下飛機，唔好霸住時事台。"},{"pid":"5315d5140046ac63803f5a1d1091155d81d78ee1","tid":661784,"uid":108201,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"396bd40f838dc76d94de016ffb329921ebf179b9","tid":661784,"uid":46896,"like":7,"dislike":9,"score":-2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T01:38:59.000Z","msg":"應該，開個台俾侵啲支持者打下飛機，唔好霸住時事台。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T02:02:46.000Z","msg":"打咩飛機？侵侵每個政策都對世界有重大影響<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15637adfd995a43492f704bb6c9ae6eaf99bef65","tid":661784,"uid":61864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5315d5140046ac63803f5a1d1091155d81d78ee1","tid":661784,"uid":108201,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"396bd40f838dc76d94de016ffb329921ebf179b9","tid":661784,"uid":46896,"like":7,"dislike":9,"score":-2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T01:38:59.000Z","msg":"應該，開個台俾侵啲支持者打下飛機，唔好霸住時事台。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T02:02:46.000Z","msg":"打咩飛機？侵侵每個政策都對世界有重大影響<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T03:03:12.000Z","msg":"的確係幾大影響<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b56b6d48eaaba1af2ab2355c5ffe5d9a0d1dbee5","tid":661784,"uid":108201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"15637adfd995a43492f704bb6c9ae6eaf99bef65","tid":661784,"uid":61864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5315d5140046ac63803f5a1d1091155d81d78ee1","tid":661784,"uid":108201,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"396bd40f838dc76d94de016ffb329921ebf179b9","tid":661784,"uid":46896,"like":7,"dislike":9,"score":-2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T01:38:59.000Z","msg":"應該，開個台俾侵啲支持者打下飛機，唔好霸住時事台。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T02:02:46.